您可以使用來檢測您的應用程式的效能負面影響降至最低陳述式，而不是使用陳述式。You can minimize the performance penalty of instrumenting your application by using  statements instead of using  statements. 下列兩個程式碼範例會將相同的偵錯訊息傳送。The following two code examples send the same debugging message. 不過，第一個範例中會更快追蹤已關閉，因為如果mySwitch.TraceError評估為，您不能呼叫。However, the first example is much faster when tracing is off, because if mySwitch.TraceError evaluates to , you do not call . 第二個範例一律會呼叫，即使mySwitch.TraceError是並會產生任何追蹤輸出。The second example always calls , even when mySwitch.TraceError is  and no tracing output is produced. 這樣可以很複雜的程式碼的不必要的執行。This can result in unnecessary execution of arbitrarily complex code.  
  
第一個範例：First example: 
```csharp  
if(mySwitch.TraceError)   
    Debug.Write("aNumber = " + aNumber + " out of range");  
```  
  
第二個範例：Second example: 
```csharp  
Debug.WriteIf(mySwitch.TraceError, "aNumber = " + aNumber + " out of range");  
```

